I have had troubles with the pawnstorms on the queenside in previous games with him. Overall our games (where I'm white) tend to be the same: I get the initiative have a good play on the centre and kingside, but his pawns on the queenside give me troubles towards the end. I pressure him hard, but use too much time thinking and end in a time trouble, where I blunder and lose the game. This game follows the pattern to some extent.
